00:02:34.299 --> 00:02:38.260
if not more important and that
sort of set the whole thing in motion. And

00:02:38.260 --> 00:02:43.569
I realized I could tell the story of
what's happening in physics and cosmology

00:02:43.569 --> 00:02:47.749
but through the eyes of a traveler
who's going around to these various places

00:02:47.749 --> 00:02:51.819
and talking about experiments rather
than the theory. I mean, the theory is very

00:02:51.819 --> 00:02:56.810
integral to the book. It -- it
makes its presence felt all over the book

00:02:56.810 --> 00:03:01.140
but the heart of the book is really
